Friday, 7 August 2015

Lucas Lee: releases third studio album - Business Brunch Specials: Uranium Omelet (with GMO-Free Brown Sauce)

Posted by: Laurie Monk at 22:25
Email ThisBlogThis!Share to TwitterShare to FacebookShare to Pinterest


Multi-instrumentalist Lucas Lee's third studio album ""Business Brunch Specials: Uranium Omelet (with GMO-Free Brown Sauce)"" has been released. Album features drumming virtuoso Tobias Ralph (The Crimson ProjeKCT, Adrian Belew Power Trio).

Preview and Purchase at CDBaby:
http://www.cdbaby.com/cd/lucaslee13

Guitars, Bass and Keys - Lucas Lee
Drums - Tobias Ralph

Recorded and Mixed by Lucas Lee in San Diego, CA
http://www.LucasLeeMusic.com

Drum performances by Tobias Ralph
www.tobiasralph.com

Mastered at Veneto West in Santa Monica, CA
by Ronan Chris Murphy
www.venetowest.com

"
Labels: Lucas Lee
